{"tid":628654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看到正妹就興奮　女慘遭公牛霸王硬上弓","createTime":"2018-04-14T05:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:08:36.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"668b1e424671b219e8f6d15e0dfce5e55a80e531","tid":628654,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"印度街頭日前有一隻公牛在街上亂竄，路上有多名男子騎著各式摩多車或腳踏車，但公牛都不為所動，不過一看到一輛機車上有正妹，公牛立刻興奮了起來，甚至霸王硬上弓。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，牛牛走在印度街頭並不奇怪，對當地人來說，牛是聖物。不過這隻公牛可能疑似處在發情期，雖說路上有許多男子騎車或走路經過，但公牛依舊不受驚擾，但當牠發現有一台白色摩托車，上面載有兩名正妹時，公牛突然激動興奮，立刻霸王硬上弓，企圖交配。兩名尾隨在後方拍片的男子，也錄下受害女子驚聲尖叫、嚇到花容失色的場景。<br />\n<br />\n隨後其他男路人發現這一幕，就協助女子趕走這頭淫蕩的公牛，而公牛在人類的驅趕下，悻悻然離開。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180414/1334253/看到正妹就興奮\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180414%2F1334253%2F%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%B0%B1%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE&d=WxIVqh6e2MKgQ83lfIU2XP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fdd671ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180414%2F1334253%2F%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%B0%B1%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE&h=c3f5acf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180414/1334253/看到正妹就興奮</a>　女慘遭公牛霸王硬上弓"},{"pid":"f86f2356f5a06678e4cd92849240b404fb0c22a0","tid":628654,"uid":126977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"聖牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca967398ece7abe7818f9cbf78c5fb21bb284e69","tid":628654,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ac672ccedb986f021c996ef37b53e12ee7318b","tid":628654,"uid":15743